summary: AN ORDINANCE carrying over the unexpended and unencumbered balances in certain 1974 Budget appropriations made from the General, Library, Seattle Center, City Street, Federal Shared Revenue, Light, Water, Sewer, Engineering Department Operating, Building Department Operating, General Services Operating, Personnel Services Operating, Urban Renewal Operating, Community Development Operating, Art Commission Operating, Employees Retirement and Public Health Revolving Funds to the respective items in the 1975 Budget.
